{"title":"告诉我，来自祖国的风","authors":["蔡庆生"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":3,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我，来自祖国的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡庆生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是祖国和平建设的哨兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫在朝鲜前线的山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼注视着分界线的南沿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心和祖国人民一起跳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和风吹过大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹过我的头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风啊！停一停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你可是来自北京？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你见过毛主席？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你见过辛勤劳动着的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你可曾带着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国工厂冒出的烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可曾带着祖国劳动竞赛中的歌声？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“祖国建设的喜讯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可带得动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国美好的景象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你能说得清？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快告诉我吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自祖国的风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天说不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天我继续听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我渴望知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大小事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕你告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“祖国又增产了一颗螺丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就等于说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“又增加了我的一分责任。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}